00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:20,680
I mean, how can I put it?

490
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:22,760
I mean, just general declarations,

491
00:27:22,760 --> 00:27:26,480
let's take the portal that Bezos has.

492
00:27:26,480 --> 00:27:29,080
I mean, that doesn't, we'll not get us anywhere.

493
00:27:29,080 --> 00:27:31,440
We need to think of incentives

494
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:35,680
for the private sector to invest in this areas

495
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:37,240
that we're interested to invest.

496
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:38,480
Thank you.

