00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:37,440
Now, maybe we need to look back at what works

516
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:41,240
in the New Deal era in the 50s and 60s.

517
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:44,240
There are some problems there, but maybe we need to go back

518
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:46,680
towards a better balance between the public

519
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:47,680
and private sector.

