1205
01:05:03,360 --> 01:05:07,480
from the public, to an entanglement

1206
01:05:07,480 --> 01:05:11,240
between corporate interests and the political interests.

1207
01:05:11,240 --> 01:05:12,440
Now, that's contentious.

