1252
01:07:30,320 --> 01:07:33,560
he wouldn't be as quick to spend money on a rocket ship

1253
01:07:33,560 --> 01:07:35,720
to take a thrill ride into space.

1254
01:07:35,720 --> 01:07:37,440
That's possible.

1255
01:07:37,440 --> 01:07:39,560
It's easier for me to imagine that response

1256
01:07:39,560 --> 01:07:43,200
than that he would back away from an otherwise profitable

1257
01:07:43,200 --> 01:07:44,440
investment.

